summary: This is an email chain from January 2021 between U.S. Attorney's Office personnel, forwarding a letter and materials related to defense submissions in the Epstein case. It indicates negotiations are at an impasse and the prosecution team is sharing defense materials to discuss next steps.
keyFacts: Email dated January 15, 2021, forwarding materials related to the Epstein case.
Negotiations between the prosecution and defense attorneys are described as being at an impasse.
The email attaches a full collection of defense submissions received from counsel.
A team memo regarding document EFTA00097609 is also attached.
All personal names and email addresses appear to be redacted (shown as placeholders like (USANYS)).
